verbose_text: Recent studies have demonstrated that several growth factor receptors involving the PI3K / Akt cascade in their signal transduction are expressed in MB, such as the insulin like growth factor-I receptor, Tropomyosin related kinase B (TrkB), Platelet derived growth factor receptor-beta (PDGFRB), and c-Kit [XREF_BIBR - XREF_BIBR].
